content: I think I'll visit Fess Parker Winery. I've heard great things about their Pinot Noir. By the way, speaking of great experiences, I had an amazing time on my last road trip to San Diego with my family. We stopped overnight at a hotel in Flagstaff, Arizona, and then spent three nights at a beachfront condo in La Jolla. The condo had an amazing view of the ocean, and we even spotted some dolphins from the balcony!
